<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 13:25:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Novogratz 的 Galaxy Digital 因加密货币溃败而遭受损失</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/novogratz-s-galaxy-digital-posts-loss-as-crypto-rout-lingers</link><description>由亿万富翁迈克尔·诺沃格拉茨 (Michael Novogratz) 创立和经营的加密金融服务集团 Galaxy Digital Inc. 公布第一季度亏损小于预期，理由是随着经常性费用收入和交易收入持续改善，业务组合中向数据中心的转变。收入高于分析师的预期。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iikdUX6WTmck/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 12:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/novogratz-s-galaxy-digital-posts-loss-as-crypto-rout-lingers</guid></item><item><title>交易员权衡伊朗问题进展，比特币触及 12 周新高</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/bitcoin-reaches-12-week-high-on-iran-deal-optimism</link><description>比特币触及 12 周高点，然后小幅回落，因为交易员消化了有关美伊谈判结束中东冲突进展的相互矛盾的迹象。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/in7uHlRB8Zek/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 04:02:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/bitcoin-reaches-12-week-high-on-iran-deal-optimism</guid></item><item><title>100 亿美元挤兑后 DeFi 救援伤害反华尔街宣传</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/defi-rescue-hurts-anti-wall-street-pitch-after-10-billion-run</link><description>去中心化金融正处于其历史上最大规模的协调救援之中，这一努力的特点是道德风险担忧和临时谈判，这与该行业作为传统金融颠覆者的创始宣传格格不入。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iMX1bkovgeE0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 18:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/defi-rescue-hurts-anti-wall-street-pitch-after-10-billion-run</guid></item><item><title>战略放缓比特币购买，转向普通销售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/strategy-slows-bitcoin-buying-switches-back-to-common-sales</link><description>Strategy Inc. 在过去 7 天购买了 2.55 亿美元的比特币，在过去两周花费了 35 亿美元之后，放慢了购买数字货币的步伐。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV72m45pZHwE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/strategy-slows-bitcoin-buying-switches-back-to-common-sales</guid></item></channel></rss>